@startuml
title SE Admin DuLieuDuKhach
actor Admin as A
participant "TravelGuide.AdminWeb/WEB/app.js async function loadTouristOverview()" as FE
participant "TravelGuide.AdminWeb/WEB/app.js const api = async (url, options)" as APIJS
participant "TravelGuide.AdminWeb/Program.cs MapGet(\"/api/tourists/overview\")" as API1
participant "TravelGuide.AdminWeb/Program.cs MapGet(\"/api/tourists/poi-scan-dashboard\")" as API2
database "TravelGuideDb.GetTouristOverviewAsync()" as DB1
database "TravelGuideDb.GetTouristPoiScanDashboardAsync()" as DB2
A -> FE : Tab dữ liệu du khách / refresh
FE -> APIJS : await api(`/api/tourists/overview?visitHistoryChartWeekStart=...`)
APIJS -> API1 : GET
API1 -> DB1 : await GetTouristOverviewAsync(visitHistoryChartWeekStart)
DB1 --> API1 : object dashboard
FE -> APIJS : await api(\"/api/tourists/poi-scan-dashboard\")
APIJS -> API2 : GET
API2 -> DB2 : await GetTouristPoiScanDashboardAsync()
DB2 --> API2 : object dashboard quét POI
FE --> A : render KPI / bảng / biểu đồ

note bottom of API2
  Cùng endpoint **GET /api/tourists/poi-scan-dashboard** được gọi thêm từ tab **Heatmap** (app.js ``refreshHeatmapTab``), không chỉ tab Dữ liệu du khách.
end note
@enduml
